I thought it would rain, but it’s all humidity here — so I skipped foundation and went for the NIVEA Luminous Serum instead.
ಇದು ಲೈಟ್ವೇಟ್ ಆಗಿದ್ದು ಸ್ಕಿನ್‌ಗೆ ತಕ್ಷಣ ಅಡಗೋದು, perfect for tropical weather! 💧

It has thiamidol which helps reduce dark spots from my face visibly within 2 weeks of usage. I always pair it up with their Luminous Day Cream which has SPF 50, so no sunscreen stress either✨
